-- RIM CEO Seeks Top 3 Spot in Mobile Computers, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-01-30T07:37:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-30/rim-ceo-seeks-top-3-spot-in-mobile-computers-handelsblatt-says.html
Research In Motion Ltd. (RIM)  Chief
Executive Officer Thorsten Heins wants his company to rank among
the top three players in the market for mobile computers in the
long run,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing an interview.  There will be “no quarter” in which the company will lose
money or run out of cash, he said, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
